content:
The process of implementing Einstein Discovery solutions typically involves a series of tasks. 

1 Define the Outcome: Define an outcome that you want to improve, likely a key performance indicator (KPI) for your business.

2 Assemble the Data: Design and populate the CRM Analytics dataset to contain the data you want to investigate.

3 Create the Model: Based on that dataset, create and configure a model that tells Einstein how to analyze your data.

4 Investigate Insights: Investigate the insights that Einstein generated during its analysis.

5 Evaluate Model Quality: Assess performance and refine the predictive model.

6 Deploy the Model: Deploy the model into Salesforce.

Predict outcomes and get improvements using the model you deployed.
title: Implementing Einstein Discovery Solutions
